creator: Bad Cat Media
descriptionHtml:
Try this ruthless, high-tempo fitness game from Bad Cat Media. Flip a card every minute - you've got 60 seconds to complete the exercise before the next card drops. With clear, simple instructions, and exercises targeting every major muscle group, you can level up your fitness any time, any place.

With the free app
+ The Classic Deck: 10 different exercises tailored for a crushing total-body workout. No equipment necessary.
+ The Classic Workout: Endless replayability. With fully randomized draws, no two workouts will ever be the same.
+ Four difficulty levels: Go light with 10 cards, medium with 25 cards, hard with 40 cards, or push your sanity to the limit with the whole deck of 55 cards.

With the Pro upgrade
+ Additional exercise decks: the Iso Deck and the Plyo Deck (coming soon!).
+ Additional workout types: the Circuit workout and the Speed Run.
+ Fully customizable difficulty levels: Fine-tune your workout with the exact number of cards you'd like to play.
+ Workout history: Track your progress and see how far you've come with a detailed calendar and a full tally of every exercise you've completed.
descriptionShort: The classic home workout game that will leave you begging for mercy.

title: Deck Of Pain

creator: Bad Cat Media
descriptionHtml:
Try this fun, high-tempo fitness game from Bad Cat Media. With clear, simple instructions, and exercises targeting every major muscle group, you can level up your fitness any time, any place.

How it works:

1) Choose your deck - this will determine what kind of exercises you get.

2) Choose the number of cards for your workout - go for something nice and quick or push your limits by attempting the entire deck.

3) Choose your intensity level - keep it light with low reps or go hard with insane reps. It's your workout, tailor it to your needs!

4) Tell us what you think - follow the link at the end of your workout to let us know how it went! We're always adding new features, and we're eager to hear how we can give you more of what you want.

We hope you enjoy your workout!

Julia & Doug

title: Oombly Arcade

creator: Oombly
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Oombly Arcade!

Here we subscribe to the radical idea that your body doesn't need to be changed!

Sure, you enjoy being active, and it feels good to get moving.

We are Here. For. That.

We enjoy being active and moving our bodies, too!

And we believe you don't need to change anything about yourself to enjoy the pleasure of moving your body and connecting with friends.

So, welcome!

Hop on in, get a game going, and have some fun.

We can't wait to get moving with you.
descriptionShort: A collection of casual exercise games focused on having fun.
